1
00:00:00,550 --> 00:00:02,322
Fares, please!
请买票!

2
00:00:02,489 --> 00:00:05,255
Trafalgar Square, please.
请买一张到Trafalgar广场的票.

3
00:00:05,629 --> 00:00:11,539
I'm sorry, sir. I can't change a ten-pound note.
对不起,我找不开10英镑的钞票.

4
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:16,019
Haven't you got any small change?
您没有零钱吗?

5
00:00:16,109 --> 00:00:20,234
I've got no small change, I am afraid.
我恐怕我没有零钱.

6
00:00:20,379 --> 00:00:23,615
I'll ask some of the passengers.
我来问问其他乘客.

7
00:00:23,832 --> 00:00:27,216
Have you any small change, sir?
先生,您有零钱吗?

8
00:00:28,086 --> 00:00:31,460
I'm sorry. I've got none.
对不起,我没有.

9
00:00:31,597 --> 00:00:34,663
I haven't got any either.
我也没有.

10
00:00:35,386 --> 00:00:40,075
Can you change this ten-pound note, madam?
夫人,您能把这10英镑的钞票换开吗?

11
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:43,436
I'm afraid I can't.
恐怕不能.

12
00:00:43,437 --> 00:00:46,066
Neither can I.
我也不能.

13
00:00:46,483 --> 00:00:48,886
I'm very sorry, sir.
非常抱歉,先生.

14
00:00:48,887 --> 00:00:51,759
You must get off the bus.
您必须下车.

15
00:00:51,830 --> 00:00:56,878
None of our passengers can change this note.
我们的乘客中没人能换开这张钞票.

16
00:00:56,879 --> 00:00:59,399
They're all millionaires!
他们都是百万富翁!

17
00:00:59,796 --> 00:01:02,269
Except us.
我们俩除外.

18
00:01:02,335 --> 00:01:05,468
I've got some small change.
我有一些零钱.

19
00:01:05,469 --> 00:01:07,396
So have I.
我也有.

